Symbol.Script_3D:
!sphere 0.01:lin_ 0,0,0,1,0,0:lin_ 0,0,0,0,2,0:lin_ 0,0,0,0,0,.5
HOTSPOT corner1, 0, 0, UnID, yCorner1, 1+128:UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner1, yCorner1, 0, UnID, yCorner1, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner1, -1, 0, UnID, yCorner1, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT 0, yCorner1, 0, UnID, corner1, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner1, yCorner1, 0, UnID, corner1, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT -1, yCorner1, 0, UnID, corner1, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT corner2, 0, 0, UnID, yCorner2, 1+128:UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner2, yCorner2, 0, UnID, yCorner2, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner2, -1, 0, UnID, yCorner2, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT 0, yCorner2, 0, UnID, corner2, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner2, yCorner2, 0, UnID, corner2, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT -1, yCorner2, 0, UnID, corner2, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT corner3, 0, 0, UnID, yCorner3, 1+128:UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner3, yCorner3, 0, UnID, yCorner3, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner3, -1, 0, UnID, yCorner3, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT 0, yCorner3, 0, UnID, corner3, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT corner3, yCorner3, 0, UnID, corner3, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT -1, yCorner3, 0, UnID, corner3, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
! ============================================================================== ! 3D Detail Level ! ==============================================================================
_iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL_3D_DETAILED call "DetlevelFunctionMacro" parameters iDetlevel3D = iDetlevel3D, returned_parameters _iDetlevel3D
if _iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL_3D_DRAFT then pen gs_cont_pen material gs_cabinet_mat
call "Schematic3DModel" parameters iFormType = 1, ! FORM_BLOCK A = A, B = B, ZZYZX = ZZYZX end endif
! Cupboard
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
if iFunctions = -1 then gosub "CupboardCompatibility" endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - END
IF _iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL_3D_OFF THEN END IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
!* 3D Hotspot unID=1
!* Total Height
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot corner1, yCorner1, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner1, yCorner1, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner1, yCorner1, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot corner2, yCorner2, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner2, yCorner2, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner2, yCorner2, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1
hotspot corner3, yCorner3, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner3, yCorner3, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1 hotspot corner3, yCorner3, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1
!!* Base Height - If bBase is off, only the base hotspot is visible, the movable isn't, hence + 128 * not (bBase) ! !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh, -1, unID, leg_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), cooh, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 + 128 * not (bBase) : unID=unID+1 ! !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh, -1, unID, leg_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), cooh, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 + 128 * not (bBase) : unID=unID+1 ! !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, -1, unID, leg_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot A-side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT), B, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 + 128 * not (bBase) : unID=unID+1 ! !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, 0, unID, leg_h, 1 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, -1, unID, leg_h, 3 : unID=unID+1 !hotspot side_overhang*(gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH | gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT), B, leg_h, unID, leg_h, 2 + 128 * not (bBase) : unID=unID+1
!!**************************************************
PEN gs_cont_pen
thickness = 0.02
lffw=a-2*side_overhang-2*thickness/2 !!! Leafs full widht lffh=zzyzx-cot-_actLeg_h-2*thickness/2 !!! Leafs full height
IF bCornice THEN corniceCorr = cot ELSE corniceCorr = 0 ENDIF
IF bBase THEN legCorr = leg_h ELSE legCorr = 0 ENDIF
put 0,0, corner2, yCorner2, corner1, yCorner1, corner3, yCorner3, 0,0
GROUP "outerSolid" material shmat PRISM 5, ZZYZX-corniceCorr-legCorr, use(nsp) ENDGROUP
xSize = max(0, corner1, corner2, corner3) - min(0, yCorner1, yCorner2, yCorner3) ySize = max(0, corner1, corner2, corner3) - min(0, yCorner1, yCorner2, yCorner3)
smallerSize = min(xSize, ySize) ratio = (smallerSize - 2*thickness) / smallerSize
xCentroid = (0 + corner3) / 2 yCentroid = (0 + yCorner3) / 2
GROUP "inCutSolid" material shmat mulz -1 mul ratio, ratio, -1 add xCentroid * (1-ratio), yCentroid * (1-ratio), thickness PRISM 5, ZZYZX-(2*thickness )-corniceCorr-legCorr, use(nsp) del 2 ENDGROUP
outShell = SUBGROUP ("outerSolid", "inCutSolid")
addZ legCorr
material shmat
PLACEGROUP outShell KILLGROUP "outerSolid"
! ----- Cornices -----
!if bCornice then ! MULX -1 ! ADDZ zzyzx-cot ! ! if cooh <= fr_th1 then ! corniceDepth = b-fr_th1 + cooh ! else ! corniceDepth = b ! endif ! ! CALL "fa_cornicetyp" PARAMETERS ALL b = corniceDepth ! ! DEL 1 ! DEL 1 !endif !!* Legs ! !if bBase then ! CALL "fa_cabinet_legtyp" PARAMETERS A = A, ! B = B-fr_th1, ! iDetlevel3D = _iDetlevel3D, ! gs_leg_type_m = gs_leg_type_m, ! leg_h = leg_h, ! leg_w = leg_w, ! cooh = cooh, ! side_overhang = side_overhang, ! gs_resol = gs_resol, ! gs_leg_mat = gs_leg_mat, ! gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ! gs_lining_m = gs_lining_m !endif ! !!* Shelves and Hangers ! !corniceRight = 0 !corniceLeft = 0 !if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT or gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then corniceRight = 1 !if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT or gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then corniceLeft = 1 !insideA = A - side_overhang*corniceRight - side_overhang*corniceLeft - 2*thickness !if iFunctions = COMBINED then ! insideTemp = insideA ! if dn >= 3 then ! insideA = ((insideA-thickness*(dn-1))/dn)*(dn-2)+thickness*(dn-3) ! else ! insideA = (insideA-thickness)/2 ! endif !endif
if iFunctions = SHELVES or iFunctions = COMBINED then if bShelves then sfh=zzyzx-cot-_actLeg_h-2*thickness !!! Shelves full height bb=(sfh+thickness)/(iNumShelves+1) ! add -a/2+thickness+side_overhang*corniceLeft, -thickness,_actLeg_h + bb if iFunctions = SHELVES then gosub "shelves" else gosub "shelves" del 1 endif del 1 endif endif
!if iFunctions = COMBINED and dn < 3 then ! add -a/2+thickness+side_overhang*corniceLeft, -thickness,_actLeg_h+thickness ! addx insideA ! material shmat ! PRISM_ 4, sfh, ! thickness,0,15, ! thickness,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, ! 0,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, ! 0,0,15 ! del 2 !endif
if iFunctions = HANGERS or iFunctions = COMBINED then material gs_hanger_mat
ADD -a/2+thickness+side_overhang*corniceLeft, -b/2, (zzyzx - cot)/10*8.5
if iFunctions = HANGERS then roty 90 GROUP "hangercyl" cylind A-(2*thickness), thickness ENDGROUP
GROUP "cylcutter" del 1 del 3 addZ thickness roty 90 addZ -0.35 addY -0.2 addX -A-(2*thickness) PRISM 5, ZZYZX, A-thickness, 0, corner1-thickness, B-thickness, 1.5*A, B-thickness, 1.5*A, 0, A-thickness, 0
ENDGROUP
hangerfinal = SUBGROUP ("hangercyl", "cylcutter")
PLACEGROUP hangerfinal PLACEGROUP "cylcutter" else addx insideTemp - insideA - thickness roty 270 GROUP "hangercyl2" cylind insideTemp - insideA -thickness, thickness ENDGROUP del 2 hangerfinal = ISECTGROUP ("inCutSolid","hangercyl2")
PLACEGROUP hangerfinal endif del 2 endif
!* Vertical panels
IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE OR not(bCornice) then valt2=-a/2+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then valt2=-a/2+side_overhang+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT then valt2=-a/2+thickness/2 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT then valt2=-a/2+side_overhang+thickness/2
vpn=CEIL(dn/2)-1
ADD valt2+(lffw2/dn)*2,-thickness,_actLeg_h+thickness
FOR i=1 TO vpn MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat PRISM_ 4, zzyzx-cot-_actLeg_h-2*thickness, thickness/2,0,15, -thickness/2,0,15, -thickness/2,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15, thickness/2,-b+fr_th1+cooh+thickness,15 ADDX (lffw2/dn)*2 NEXT i DEL vpn DEL 1
!* Leafs if DoorEnable = 1 THEN aRot = atn(yCorner3 / corner3)
rotz aRot mulx sqr(yCorner3 ** 2 + corner3 ** 2) / lffw2 FOR i=1 TO dn call "fa_warddoortyp" parameters all bNotMacro = 0, gs_full_edit = 0, bAngleEdit = 0, bMirrored = 0, bFormMirror = 0, bSliding = 0, iDoorStyle = iDoorStyle, iTempDoorStyle = iDoorStyle, bBevel = gs_bevel, doorThickness = fr_th1, doorFrameWidth = doorframe_w, mullionWidth = 0.016, nVerticalMullion = vert_gnum, nHorizontalMullion = hor_gnum, matDoorFrame = doorframe_mat, matDoorGlass = doorglas_mat, matDoorMirror = doorglas_mat, matDoorDecor1 = doorframe_mat, matDoorDecor2 = doorframe_mat, doorWidth = lffw2/dn, doorHeight = lffh, doorCustomPanelName = gs_cust_p, bKnob = 0, doorAngle3D = 0
ADDX lffw2/dn NEXT i DEL dn DEL 2 ENDIF
!* Knobs on leafs
if bKnob & _bDrawKnob & DoorEnable then aRot = atn(yCorner3 / corner3)
rotz aRot
valt=-a/2+side_overhang+thickness/2 if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT then valt=-a/2+thickness/2 if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT then valt=-a/2+side_overhang+thickness/2 if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE then valt=-a/2+thickness/2
! add valt,-b+cooh,_actLeg_h+thickness/2 !sphere .1:lin_ 0,0,0,1,0,0:lin_ 0,0,0,0,2,0:lin_ 0,0,0,0,0,.5 if iKnobPlacing = KNOB_POS_VER or gs_knob_type_m = KNOB_STYLE_1 or \ gs_knob_type_m = KNOB_STYLE_2 or \ gs_knob_type_m = KNOB_STYLE_3 then temp = 0 else temp = knob_size endif
if INT(dn/2)<>dn/2 then add lffw2-lffw2/dn+knob_pl_x+temp, -fr_th1, knob_pl_y call "fa_knobtyp" parameters all iDetlevel3D = _iDetlevel3D
add -temp, 0, -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
addx -knob_pl_x - temp hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1 del 1 endif
h_knob=1-_actLeg_h-thickness/2
_ratio = sqr(yCorner3 ** 2 + corner3 ** 2) / lffw2
add _ratio * lffw2/dn-(doorframe_w-fr_th1)/2*0,0,knob_pl_y
for k=1 to INT(dn/2) for s=1 to 2 add knob_pl_x + temp,-fr_th1,0
call "fa_knobtyp" parameters all iDetlevel3D = _iDetlevel3D
add -temp, 0, -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
addx -knob_pl_x - temp hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
del 1 mulx -1 ! add -(doorframe_w-fr_th1)-knob_pl_x+0.05,fr_th1,0 next s del 2 add lffw2/dn*2,0,0 next k del INT(dn)/2 del 1
if dn/2-int(dn/2)<0.001 then del 1
if dn<>1 then del 1 del 1 endif
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! end !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
"shelves": for i=1 to iNumShelves material shmat
mul ratio, ratio, 1 add xCentroid * (1-ratio), yCentroid * (1-ratio), thickness PRISM nsp/2, 0.015, use(nsp) del 2 addz bb next i del iNumShelves return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Cupboard.gsm
! ============================================================================== ! 2D Detail Level ! ==============================================================================
hotspot2 0, 0, UnID :UnID = UnID + 1 !hotspot2 A, 0, UnID :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 corner1, 0, UnID, yCorner1, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner1, yCorner1, UnID, yCorner1, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner1, -1, UnID, yCorner1, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 0, yCorner1, UnID, corner1, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner1, yCorner1, UnID, corner1, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 -1, yCorner1, UnID, corner1, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 corner2, 0, UnID, yCorner2, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner2, yCorner2, UnID, yCorner2, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner2, -1, UnID, yCorner2, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 0, yCorner2, UnID, corner2, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner2, yCorner2, UnID, corner2, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 -1, yCorner2, UnID, corner2, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 corner3, 0, UnID, yCorner3, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner3, yCorner3, UnID, yCorner3, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner3, -1, UnID, yCorner3, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
HOTSPOT2 0, yCorner3, UnID, corner3, 1+128 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 corner3, yCorner3, UnID, corner3, 2 :UnID = UnID + 1 HOTSPOT2 -1, yCorner3, UnID, corner3, 3 :UnID = UnID + 1
if TopCross = 1 THEN pen ContourPen line2 0, 0, corner1, yCorner1 line2 corner3, yCorner3, corner2, yCorner2 endif
pen FillPen
set fill TopFill poly2 5, 3, 0, 0, corner2, yCorner2, corner1, yCorner1, corner3, yCorner3, 0, 0
_iDetlevel2D = iDetlevel2D call "DetlevelFunctionMacro" parameters iDetlevel2D = iDetlevel2D, returned_parameters _iDetlevel2D
if _iDetlevel2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SYMBOLIC then _iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle else if _iDetlevel2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then _iSymbolStyle = 7 if _iDetlevel2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then _iSymbolStyle = 6 if _iDetlevel2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DRAFT then _iSymbolStyle = 1 endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
!if iFunctions = -1 then ! gosub "CupboardCompatibility" !endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - END PEN gs_cont_pen
!CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** Minimal space *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 1, unID = 3000
!!!Functions
!if bHangers and\ ! (_iSymbolStyle <> 2 and\ ! _iSymbolStyle <> 3 and\ ! _iSymbolStyle <> 4 and\ ! _iSymbolStyle <> 5) then ! if iFunctions = HANGERS then ! LINE2 0,b/2,a,b/2 ! tempA = a ! gosub "hangers" ! endif ! ! if iFunctions = COMBINED then ! if dn >= 3 then ! insideA = (A/dn)*(dn-2) ! else ! insideA = A/2 ! LINE2 a/2,0,a/2,b ! endif ! ! LINE2 insideA,b/2,A,b/2 ! ADD2 insideA,0 ! LINE2 0,0,0,b ! tempA = a-insideA ! gosub "hangers" ! DEL 1 ! endif !endif
!!! 2D Symbol
!call "cabSymbolType" parameters all bSeparateCabinets = 1, ! nDoor = dn, ! doorThickness = fr_th1, ! openingAngle2D = opa2, ! iSymbolStyle = _iSymbolStyle
END
"hangers": ADD2 0.2, (b-0.025)/2 hn = tempA - 2*0.1 cn=INT(hn/0.15) FOR ii=1 TO cn ff=rnd(.2) ROT2 ff*100 line2 -0.025, -0.2, 0.025, 0.2 DEL 1 ADD2 0.15, 0 NEXT ii DEL cn del 1 return
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL_3D_MVO = 1 DETLEVEL_3D_SCSENS = 2 DETLEVEL_3D_DETAILED = 3 DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE = 4 DETLEVEL_3D_DRAFT = 5 DETLEVEL_3D_OFF = 6
! const values for iDetlevel2D DETLEVEL_2D_MVO = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_SCSENS = 2 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 3 DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 4 DETLEVEL_2D_DRAFT = 5 DETLEVEL_2D_SYMBOLIC = 6
EPS=0.0001
DIM stFunctions[3] stFunctions[1] = `Shelves` stFunctions[2] = `Hangers` stFunctions[3] = `Combined`
! const values for parameter: iFunctions SHELVES = 1 HANGERS = 2 COMBINED = 3
dim stDoorStyle[11] stDoorStyle[1] = `Style 1` stDoorStyle[2] = `Style 2` stDoorStyle[3] = `Style 3` stDoorStyle[4] = `Style 4` stDoorStyle[5] = `Style 5` stDoorStyle[6] = `Style 6` stDoorStyle[7] = `Style 7` stDoorStyle[8] = `Style 8` stDoorStyle[9] = `Style 9` stDoorStyle[10] = `Style 10` stDoorStyle[11] = `Custom Panel`
! const values for parameter: iDoorStyle DOOR_STYLE_1 = 1 DOOR_STYLE_2 = 2 DOOR_STYLE_3 = 3 DOOR_STYLE_4 = 11 DOOR_STYLE_5 = 12 DOOR_STYLE_6 = 9 DOOR_STYLE_7 = 4 DOOR_STYLE_8 = 5 DOOR_STYLE_9 = 6 DOOR_STYLE_10 = 7 DOOR_STYLE_CUST = 10
! const values for parameter: gs_leg_type_m LEG_STYLE_1 = 1 LEG_STYLE_2 = 2 LEG_STYLE_3 = 3 LEG_STYLE_4 = 4 LEG_STYLE_5 = 5 LEG_STYLE_6 = 6
! const values for parameter: gs_cornice_type_m CORN_STYLE_1 = 1 CORN_STYLE_2 = 2 CORN_STYLE_3 = 3 CORN_STYLE_4 = 4
! const values for parameter: gs_knob_type_m KNOB_STYLE_1 = 1 KNOB_STYLE_2 = 2 KNOB_STYLE_3 = 3 KNOB_STYLE_4 = 4 KNOB_STYLE_5 = 5 KNOB_STYLE_6 = 6 KNOB_STYLE_7 = 7 KNOB_STYLE_8 = 8
dim stLiningSide[4] stLiningSide[1] = `Front and Both Side` stLiningSide[2] = `Front and Left Side` stLiningSide[3] = `Front and Right Side` stLiningSide[4] = `Front`
! const values for parameter: gs_lining_m LINING_SIDE_BOTH = 1 LINING_SIDE_LEFT = 2 LINING_SIDE_RIGHT = 3 LINING_SIDE_NONE = 4
lffw2 = A-2*0.01 IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_BOTH then lffw2 = lffw2-2*side_overhang IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_LEFT then lffw2 = lffw2-side_overhang IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_RIGHT then lffw2 = lffw2-side_overhang IF gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE OR not(bCornice) then lffw2 = lffw2
if not(bCornice) then cot=0 cooh=0 side_overhang=0 endif
IF cot=0 THEN cooh=0 ENDIF
if bBase then _actLeg_h = leg_h else _actLeg_h = 0 endif
_bDrawKnob = 1
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL_3D_SIMPLE then vert_gnum=0 hor_gnum=0 _bDrawKnob = 0 endif
!iKnobPlacing KNOB_POS_VER = 0 KNOB_POS_HOR = 1
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
goto "MasterEnd"
"CupboardCompatibility": iFunctions = SHELVES return
"MasterEnd": ![#COMPATIBILITY] - END

Symbol.Script_VL:
![#COMPATIBILITY] - START
if iFunctions = -1 then bDefaultElem = (GLOB_INTGUID = "" | GLOB_INTGUID = "{00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000}")
if bDefaultElem then gosub "CupboardCompatibility" else iFunctions = SHELVES endif parameters iFunctions = iFunctions endif
![#COMPATIBILITY] - END
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX", "TopCross", "TopFill", "FillPen", "ContourPen", "DoorEnable"
call "FM_types" parameters all
! Custom Elements -------------------------------------
dim gs_pt[] if iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_CUST then call "Object_Panel_Collection" parameters returned_parameters gs_pt values "gs_cust_p" gs_pt endif
! ----------------------------------------------
VALUES "gs_functions" stFunctions VALUES "iFunctions" 1,2,3
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_functions" then iFunctions = SHELVES if gs_functions = stFunctions[2] then iFunctions = HANGERS if gs_functions = stFunctions[3] then iFunctions = COMBINED parameters iFunctions = iFunctions else gs_functions = stFunctions[1] if iFunctions = HANGERS then gs_functions = stFunctions[2] if iFunctions = COMBINED then gs_functions = stFunctions[3] parameters gs_functions = gs_functions endif
if iFunctions = HANGERS then lock "iNumShelves", "shmat", "bShelves" hideparameter "iNumShelves", "shmat", "bShelves" endif if not(bShelves) then lock "iNumShelves", "shmat" endif
! Enable all Symbol Types iSymbolStyleEnable = 2**1 + 2**2 + 2**3 + 2**4 + 2**5 + 2**6 + 2**7 + 2**8 + 2**9 call "cabSymbolType" parameters iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle, iSymbolStyleEnable = iSymbolStyleEnable
if iFunctions = SHELVES then lock "gs_hanger_mat" hideparameter "gs_hanger_mat" endif
if iFunctions = 1 | iFunctions = 3 |\ iSymbolStyle = 2 |\ iSymbolStyle = 3 |\ iSymbolStyle = 4 |\ iSymbolStyle = 5 then ! Lock Hanger Symbol in case of symbols drawn in the cabinet
lock "bHangers" endif
if iSymbolStyle <> 8 &\ ! Lock Door Opening Angle if the Symbol has no opening doors iSymbolStyle <> 9 then
lock "opa2" hideparameter "opa2" else values "opa2" range [0, 270] endif
! VALUES for iDetlevel3D and/or iDetlevel2D call "DetlevelFunctionMacro" parameters bEnable3DFunction = 1, iFlagEnable3DSymbols = 1 + 4 + 8 + 16 + 32, bEnable2DFunction = 1, iFlagEnable2DSymbols = 1 + 32
if iDetlevel2D <> DETLEVEL_2D_SYMBOLIC then lock "iSymbolStyle" endif
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
if not(bCornice) then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_cornice_type_m", "gs_lining_m","cot","cooh","side_overhang","gs_cornice_mat" LOCK "gs_cornice_type_m", "gs_lining_m","cot","cooh","side_overhang","gs_cornice_mat" endif
if not(bBase) then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_leg_type_m", "leg_h","leg_w","gs_leg_mat" LOCK "gs_leg_type_m", "leg_h","leg_w","gs_leg_mat" ENDIF
values{2} "gs_knob_type_m" KNOB_STYLE_1, `Style 1`, KNOB_STYLE_2, `Style 2`, KNOB_STYLE_3, `Style 3`, KNOB_STYLE_4, `Style 4`, KNOB_STYLE_5, `Style 5`, KNOB_STYLE_6, `Style 6`, KNOB_STYLE_7, `Style 7`, KNOB_STYLE_8, `Style 8`
if not(bKnob) then hideparameter "gs_knob_type_m", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "iKnobPlacing", "knob_size", "gs_knob_mat" lock "gs_knob_type_m", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "iKnobPlacing", "knob_size", "gs_knob_mat" endif
dim st_knobplacing[2] st_knobplacing[1]=`Vertical` st_knobplacing[2]=`Horizontal`
values{2} "iKnobPlacing", KNOB_POS_VER, `Vertical`, KNOB_POS_HOR, `Horizontal`
if iDoorStyle <> DOOR_STYLE_CUST then hideparameter "gs_cust_p" lock "gs_cust_p" endif
values "leg_h" range [0,) values "leg_w" range (0,) values "dn" range [1,) values "doorframe_w" range [0.01,) values "iNumShelves" range [1,) values "cot" range (0,) values "vert_gnum" range [0,) values "hor_gnum" range [0,) values "gs_resol" range [3,) values "fr_th1" range [0.01,) xKnobPosMod = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = KNOB_STYLE_4 & iKnobPlacing = KNOB_POS_HOR then xKnobPosMod = knob_size * 128/100 if gs_knob_type_m > 4 & iKnobPlacing = KNOB_POS_HOR then xKnobPosMod = knob_size values "knob_pl_x" range [0.02, lffw2/dn - 0.02 - xKnobPosMod] yKnobPosMod = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = KNOB_STYLE_4 & iKnobPlacing = KNOB_POS_VER then yKnobPosMod = knob_size * 128/100 if gs_knob_type_m > 4 & iKnobPlacing = KNOB_POS_VER then yKnobPosMod = knob_size values "knob_pl_y" range [0.02 + yKnobPosMod, zzyzx-cot-_actLeg_h-2*0.01 - 0.02] values "knob_size" range [0.045, )
if bCornice then
if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_1 then values "cooh" range [0,) if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_2 or gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_3 then values "cooh" range [1/2*cot,) if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_4 then values "cooh" range [3/4*cot,)
if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_1 then values "side_overhang" range [0,A/2 - 0.02) if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_2 or gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_3 then values "side_overhang" range [1/2*cot,A/2 - 0.02) if gs_cornice_type_m = CORN_STYLE_4 then values "side_overhang" range [3/4*cot,A/2 - 0.02)
endif
if not(bCornice) then LOCK "cooh","side_overhang","gs_lining_m" HIDEPARAMETER "cooh","side_overhang","gs_lining_m" endif
if gs_lining_m = LINING_SIDE_NONE then HIDEPARAMETER "side_overhang" LOCK "side_overhang" endif
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** Parameters Values for Macro
VALUES{2} "gs_lining_m" LINING_SIDE_BOTH, stLiningSide[1], LINING_SIDE_LEFT, stLiningSide[2], LINING_SIDE_RIGHT, stLiningSide[3], LINING_SIDE_NONE, stLiningSide[4]
values{2} "gs_leg_type_m" LEG_STYLE_1, `Style 1`, LEG_STYLE_2, `Style 2`, LEG_STYLE_3, `Style 3`, LEG_STYLE_4, `Style 4`, LEG_STYLE_5, `Style 5`, LEG_STYLE_6, `Style 6`
values{2} "gs_cornice_type_m" CORN_STYLE_1, `Style 1`, CORN_STYLE_2, `Style 2`, CORN_STYLE_3, `Style 3`, CORN_STYLE_4, `Style 4`
VALUES{2} "iDoorStyle" DOOR_STYLE_1, stDoorStyle[1], DOOR_STYLE_2, stDoorStyle[2], DOOR_STYLE_3, stDoorStyle[3], DOOR_STYLE_4, stDoorStyle[4], DOOR_STYLE_5, stDoorStyle[5], DOOR_STYLE_6, stDoorStyle[6], DOOR_STYLE_7, stDoorStyle[7], DOOR_STYLE_8, stDoorStyle[8], DOOR_STYLE_9, stDoorStyle[9], DOOR_STYLE_10, stDoorStyle[10], DOOR_STYLE_CUST, stDoorStyle[11]
if iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_1 then lock "doorframe_w","hor_gnum","vert_gnum","doorglas_mat" hideparameter "doorframe_w","hor_gnum","vert_gnum","doorglas_mat" endif if iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_2 or iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_4 or iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_7 or iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_9 or iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_CUST then lock "hor_gnum","vert_gnum","doorglas_mat" hideparameter "hor_gnum","vert_gnum","doorglas_mat" endif if iDoorStyle = DOOR_STYLE_6 then lock "hor_gnum","vert_gnum" hideparameter "hor_gnum","vert_gnum" endif
if gs_knob_type_m=KNOB_STYLE_1 or gs_knob_type_m=KNOB_STYLE_2 or gs_knob_type_m=KNOB_STYLE_3 or not(bKnob) then lock "iKnobPlacing", "knob_size" hideparameter "iKnobPlacing", "knob_size" endif !!! ******************************** Minimal Space if MSFront < 0 then MSFront = 0 parameters MSFront = MSFront endif
! ============================================================================= ! UI Support ! =============================================================================
if GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID < 0 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = -GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID endif
